title: Sound On: Colonial Cyberhack, Cheney Vote

description:
Guests: Max Burns, Democratic Strategist and Founder of Third Degree Strategies. Bloomberg's David Westin spoke to Energy Secretary Jennifer Granholm about President Biden's clean energy goals and the Colonial Pipeline cyberhack.
